
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button from 'Contrast enhanced' box on Page 03
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Mamma' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Anisomasty' radio button is enabled
And 'Ablatio' radio button is enabled
And 'Breast augmentation' radio button is enabled
And 'Thickened' checkbox is enabled
And 'Blurred' checkbox is enabled
And 'Focus' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Anisomasty' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Ablatio' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Breast augmentation' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Thickened' checkbox
Then multiple selection localizer is enabled
When I click on all parts of 'R' on the localizer
Then all parts of 'R' on the localizer are selected
When I click on all parts of 'L' on the localizer
Then all parts of 'L' on the localizer are selected

When I select 'Blurred' checkbox
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Focus' checkbox
Then multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Size' input field is enabled
And 'Round' radio button is enabled
And 'Oval' radio button is enabled
And 'Irregular' radio button is enabled
And 'Margin' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Calcification' checkbox is enabled
And 'None' radio button is enabled
And 'Mild' radio button is enabled
And 'Marked' radio button is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled

When I click on all parts of 'R' on the localizer
Then all parts of 'R' on the localizer are selected
When I click on all parts of 'L' on the localizer
Then all parts of 'L' on the localizer are selected
